        <source>Deleting the app removes all local data from your device. If you used iCloud sync, you can delete the synced data at any time via iOS <x id="START_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;strong&gt;"/>Settings → iCloud → Manage Storage<x id="CLOSE_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;/strong&gt;"/>.</source>
