      <trans-unit id="privacy.s10.p1" datatype="html">
        <source>Because the developer is established in France, the <x id="START_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;strong&gt;"/>GDPR applies to all users<x id="CLOSE_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;/strong&gt;"/>, wherever you are located. You may exercise at any time your rights of <x id="START_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;strong&gt;"/>access, rectification, erasure, portability, restriction of processing, and objection<x id="CLOSE_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;/strong&gt;"/> by emailing <x id="START_LINK" ctype="x-a" equiv-text="&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:codebygaetan@gmail.com&quot;&gt;"/>codebygaetan@gmail.com<x id="CLOSE_LINK" ctype="x-a" equiv-text="&lt;/a&gt;"/>. Note that since all workout data lives on your device or in your private iCloud, you already hold direct control over it.</source>
        <context-group purpose="location">
